05:03.886 --> 05:05.804
Nothing?

05:07.264 --> 05:11.184
Nevermind. You are a bore.

05:14.187 --> 05:19.109
So will your boss to buy Peaches?

05:19.192 --> 05:22.904
Probably. The family Dumar has shown some interest.

05:22.987 --> 05:27.533
They will probably push up the price in the bidding against Bonnie.

05:27.617 --> 05:30.244
