05:30.328 --> 05:35.416
My partner. Bonnie Brae, which owns Brae Valley Farms?

05:35.499 --> 05:38.210
It is not far from my home.

05:38.294 --> 05:43.298
Bonnie looking for a new stallion and your boy look promising.

05:43.382 --> 05:48.303
By the way, did you know who I was when you questioned my ability?

05:50.347 --> 05:53.808
Sorry, I'm not talking eye rolling.

05:55.351 --> 05:57.729
Excuse me.

05:57.812 --> 06:01.816
Fish for compliments? It is quite ridiculous.

06:01.899 --> 06:07.697
You know very well that everyone in the industry know who Jonathan Collier.

06:07.780 --> 06:11.200
But you are not a part of the industry, right?

06:11.283 --> 06:17.081
- You are a stole lapa, a suede square brownie. - I'm a rider.

06:17.164 --> 06:21.043
No. You were a rider when you won the Virginia Junior Championship.

06:21.126 --> 06:27.174
