06:27.257 --> 06:31.720
- Who really do not like you, and please tell it to others.

06:31.803 --> 06:34.222
Nowadays...

06:35.723 --> 06:39.477
... Shoveling manure and you smoke when you are alone on the job.

06:39.560 --> 06:43.981
