07:29.900 --> 07:33.820
If you had wanted to ride, you had found a solution.

07:33.904 --> 07:39.534
Instead shoveling manure to smoke on, and blame everything on your surroundings.

07:40.952 --> 07:42.704
What do you know about it?

07:42.954 --> 07:45.415
I know there are horses that you can buy.

07:45.498 --> 07:49.586
