08:12.149 --> 08:16.111
Of course, it is provided that you have saved salary.

08:17.737 --> 08:20.281
Should I interpret that as a no?

08:50.394 --> 08:52.562
63 lousy bucks.

09:08.202 --> 09:10.663
Debi! Stay!

09:12.915 --> 09:15.876
- They want to meet you at the equestrian course. - What?

09:15.960 --> 09:21.965
After yesterday, I would worry more for the "why" than the "what"?

09:22.049 --> 09:24.635
Come on! Hurry up!

09:24.760 --> 09:29.306
- Are you sure about this, Jonathan? - I need to see what he is capable of.

09:29.389 --> 09:33.476
But Jonathan, we have the most skilled riders.

09:33.560 --> 09:37.063
The girl can ride. - You said she could ride.

09:37.147 --> 09:41.359
Four years ago, on a horse that approached the tomb.

09:41.442 --> 09:46.280
And yet she defeated you. I want to see what she can do with a real horse.

09:48.157 --> 09:50.785
You wanted to see me, Mr Blue.

09:50.868 --> 09:54.538
- That's right ... excuse? - Debi.

09:54.622 --> 10:00.377
Of course, Debi. Mr Collier wanted to ask if we could ...

10:00.627 --> 10:04.464
One can learn a lot from watching someone else ride.

10:06.133 --> 10:10.428
