10:15.808 --> 10:20.021
You may be right, Monty. We should get a real horseman.

10:20.104 --> 10:24.734
I can handle it. I said, "I can handle it."

10:26.068 --> 10:27.778
Ferment? Are you sure?

10:29.363 --> 10:31.031
Okay.

10:33.951 --> 10:37.537
It is best not to take any risks, in spite of your thick skull.

10:39.331 --> 10:41.958
Need help, Debi?

