10:50.341 --> 10:52.176
Get up!

10:54.971 --> 10:57.431
This should be good.

11:22.998 --> 11:26.334
Pilar, did you know that the girl was so proficient?

11:26.417 --> 11:30.004
I did not even know that she worked for us before yesterday.

11:37.845 --> 11:40.806
It's a shame that she could not compete.

11:40.931 --> 11:46.311
Jumping is not for the mob. Therefore invented roller derby.

11:46.395 --> 11:48.355
She is the reason why ...

11:58.448 --> 12:02.035
Monty, how about $ 40,000?

12:03.161 --> 12:05.788
I will return.

12:05.872 --> 12:09.542
40,000 sounds like a fair offer.

12:09.625 --> 12:12.670
Next time I'll bring my own helmet.

12:14.171 --> 12:18.175
I knew someone would discover how cruel you are -

12:18.259 --> 12:21.887
- And buy yourself while breaking my heart.

12:21.970 --> 12:27.017
You're a real sweetie who let them do it.

12:29.102 --> 12:34.274
It is foolish to waste your talent because you're pissed off at the world.

12:34.357 --> 12:37.485
"My dad can not afford my dream horse."

12:37.569 --> 12:40.363
"The other girls are mean."

12:41.948 --> 12:43.908
What?

12:43.992 --> 12:47.703
You love the particular sound of your own voice.

12:49.121 --> 12:53.209
- Do you do anything other than talk? - I assure you ...

12:53.292 --> 12:56.337
Make sure not care about anything, Ken.

12:56.420 --> 13:01.717
Help me be better if you are so convinced of my talent.

13:01.800 --> 13:07.222
Help me. Train me if I can find a horse.

13:07.305 --> 13:11.518
Everyone knows that you are the chief of finding rider's hidden talents.

13:11.601 --> 13:15.688
So help me find my hidden talents.

13:15.772 --> 13:22.445
That said: You love the sound of your voice, but has no substance.

13:22.528 --> 13:26.824
Do you know how much I take to train a rider?

13:27.116 --> 13:30.244
How would you be able to afford my services?

13:30.327 --> 13:34.039
I'm good at what I do, but I does not conduct charity.

13:34.123 --> 13:37.584
I want to get paid for the effort.

13:37.668 --> 13:43.215
Okay sure. I can work on your farm. Whatever ...

13:43.298 --> 13:47.385
Stop messing around. A lifetime mockande is not enough for my fees.

14:00.857 --> 14:02.483
Okay.

14:04.568 --> 14:07.279
- What do you mean "okay"? - Okay then.

14:09.532 --> 14:14.078
- Are you serious? - Seriously.

14:14.161 --> 14:17.289
We'll see if you can handle it.

14:27.298 --> 14:31.469
He's not wrong. Many fine horses sold away.

14:31.719 --> 14:34.555
Horses with fine pedigrees.

14:34.806 --> 14:39.810
Just rotten, miserable owners who should never have been allowed to approach a horse.

14:40.061 --> 14:43.606
- Broken down horses. - In need of salvation.

14:43.689 --> 14:48.068
- As we all are. - Do not start that again.

14:48.152 --> 14:53.949
Maybe I need to be saved. I ran and I hid myself.

14:54.074 --> 14:58.120
It was difficult and I had to tough for me.

14:58.203 --> 15:02.332
We can check the horse market. I can help you in the right direction.

15:02.415 --> 15:05.877
I do not need your help. I can choose my own horse.

15:06.169 --> 15:11.007
I know exactly what I'm after. An independent talent.

15:11.090 --> 15:15.553
- Really? Was that all? - And a lion's heart.

15:16.929 --> 15:23.185
Do you think it's funny? He's out there and I'll find him.

15:23.269 --> 15:26.021
I just hope he does not cost more than 63 dollars.

16:24.660 --> 16:30.207
Come back here, you bastard, otherwise you'll see!

16:30.291 --> 16:33.377
Come back here!

16:35.254 --> 16:37.965
Your hell horse! I'm going to notice you!

16:39.550 --> 16:44.930
And if I had seen a burning bush, I had downloaded water hose.

17:24.760 --> 17:30.515
Then I heard it. Sweet as the wine at Cana, bright as the burning bush.

17:31.766 --> 17:37.480
The miracle of the Lord's voice. And like a child, I thought again.

17:40.733 --> 17:42.610
Come back here!

17:44.612 --> 17:47.698
Your freaking hell horse!

17:47.781 --> 17:52.536
I would shoot you if it were not a waste of bullets.

17:52.619 --> 17:56.331
Is this your horse? Is he for sale?

17:56.415 --> 18:02.546
He was there, but I received no bids. And after this teaches not enter.

18:02.629 --> 18:07.967
It would be a shame to have to sell him to the butcher.

18:08.051 --> 18:11.429
- You can not do it. - Why not, honey?

18:11.679 --> 18:15.349
- You just do not get it. - Do you have anything to say?

18:15.433 --> 18:21.439
Let's go. I know you hear what I say.

18:27.027 --> 18:31.031
- Why would the Lord speak to me? - Why not?

18:31.115 --> 18:34.076
Was not as "priestly".

18:35.369 --> 18:41.124
I heard it loud and clear, so I must have been crazy.

18:41.207 --> 18:45.086
Can I have had a brain tumor like in the movies?

18:45.170 --> 18:49.882
I would rather believe that the Lord spoke to me than that I had a tumor.

18:49.966 --> 18:55.721
Why do you think the Lord asked you to buy this horse?

18:55.805 --> 19:00.267
Or any horse at all? The Lord may have a purpose for you.

19:00.351 --> 19:04.188
- I'm not an evangelist, Father. - Maybe not.

19:04.313 --> 19:09.526
But this horse maybe it is. Are you going to buy him?

19:09.610 --> 19:14.698
At the moment I miss about half of the money.

19:14.781 --> 19:18.785
And it is with the help of my friend Tommy and an attendant that I know.

19:18.868 --> 19:23.873
So I hope that the Lord has a plan for me no fucking ...

19:23.957 --> 19:29.545
- ... Damn plane. - Let me see if I understand everything.

19:29.629 --> 19:35.801
The Lord gave you the opportunity to ride. He gave you the strength to jump.

19:35.885 --> 19:39.972
He gave you the insight to find a very special horse.

19:40.055 --> 19:44.726
And now I hope you are in a magical way to pay for it too?

19:44.810 --> 19:49.940
I was hoping you could pray with me and ask the Lord if he could ...

19:50.023 --> 19:52.818
- No. - No?

19:52.901 --> 19:55.236
It is your prayer, Miss Debi.

19:55.362 --> 20:00.575
But before you ask for more you should show gratitude for what you already got.

20:00.658 --> 20:06.038
You do not need a miracle to achieve your goals. You are the miracle.

20:06.122 --> 20:12.378
All you have to do is put you in the saddle and start riding again.

20:32.772 --> 20:37.777
It was not the first time that I asked. But it was the first time in years.

20:37.860 --> 20:43.491
First time since I moved from Nutbush, Virginia.

20:57.546 --> 20:59.715
- Debi? - Hi!

20:59.798 --> 21:05.178
- Debi, little girl! - Hi mom. I've missed you!

21:05.262 --> 21:09.057
Hey! I've missed you!

21:09.140 --> 21:14.729
- Will you finally move home? - Stop it, you know it will not happen.

21:18.483 --> 21:21.485
Let's see if I understand.

21:21.569 --> 21:26.073
Lord asked you to go home and fix money from your mom ... -

21:26.157 --> 21:31.537
- ... To buy an old nag? - He's not a nag.

21:34.498 --> 21:37.876
- Can you paint over there? - Sure.

21:39.336 --> 21:42.339
- Love you. - I love you too.

21:44.716 --> 21:47.886
I understand there is a lot to take in.

21:47.969 --> 21:53.558
But the Lord gave me my skills and a mission to complete.

21:53.766 --> 21:56.352
And the horse? Two years, Debi.

21:56.435 --> 22:01.190
You have wasted two years of your life by shoveling shit for rich people.

22:01.273 --> 22:07.363
I thought that maybe you made something and was ready to study further.

22:07.446 --> 22:13.827
That you were ready to find a job, to earn your livelihood.

22:13.911 --> 22:18.290
Do you think it's easy for me to come here and ask for help?

22:25.672 --> 22:30.301
- I know the Lord ... - The Lord wants you to do what?

22:30.385 --> 22:35.681
Savior all rich girls who have always looked down on you?

22:35.765 --> 22:40.478
Or preaching to all illiterate who work in the stables -

22:40.728 --> 22:46.442
- And do not have other thoughts than how to get you in bed.

22:48.318 --> 22:51.530
I do not know what the Lord wants of me.

22:51.613 --> 22:57.702
I just know that he wants me to do it through my jumping.

22:58.662 --> 23:02.332
And you think this horse is necessary?

23:02.624 --> 23:05.501
Do not encourage her, Margaret.

23:05.752 --> 23:10.548
I do. I have already saved up booklets.

23:10.631 --> 23:16.470
Tommy helped me and even Pastor Brewer gave me $ 100!

23:16.595 --> 23:21.767
- Larry, if a pastor ... - I do not care what the country bumpkin think!

23:31.526 --> 23:37.240
I'm not the villain here. I know what it can do against a -

23:37.323 --> 23:41.619
- When trying to get into a world that does not want one.

23:41.703 --> 23:47.917
How do you think I felt when the Redskins finished my contract?

23:48.000 --> 23:52.880
How difficult do you think it was to return and train school football?

23:52.963 --> 23:56.258
From the top back to school!

23:59.344 --> 24:03.265
Debi, darling, you're my little girl. I love you more than ...

24:05.350 --> 24:07.894
But you're too stubborn!

24:07.978 --> 24:14.943
It hurts to see you throw yourself against the wall until nothing is left.

24:16.319 --> 24:21.324
So you think it's better not to try to achieve their dreams?

24:21.407 --> 24:24.327
How is it better for me?

24:27.830 --> 24:30.416
This is how it is:

24:30.499 --> 24:34.753
Two years ago, you went away when I told -

24:34.837 --> 24:38.799
- That we could not afford to buy a Sunday horse for $ 100,000.

24:38.882 --> 24:43.804
But your mother and I have put money aside for two years at the university.

24:43.887 --> 24:47.933
So when you are ready to take your head out of your ...

24:50.435 --> 24:54.772
... Out of the clouds and start thinking about your future -

24:54.856 --> 25:01.153
- Waiting for the money to you. Until then, this conversation is over.

25:14.416 --> 25:17.711
He will never change, right?

25:17.794 --> 25:20.589
Do you think the Lord has plans for Debi?

25:20.714 --> 25:25.135
I believe the Lord has plans for all of us.

25:25.218 --> 25:29.264
But not everyone can be the occasion.

26:16.976 --> 26:20.354
I'm not the same girl anymore.

26:20.437 --> 26:24.400
The girl he sees when he looks at me. I'm not her anymore.

26:25.943 --> 26:29.780
I have changed. If it were not for this horse -

26:29.863 --> 26:35.452
- I would still save to buy a horse.

26:35.535 --> 26:40.040
I'm trying to say that I was meant to be with this horse.

26:44.711 --> 26:49.590
- Can you say something? - I would like to see this horse.

27:12.946 --> 27:17.242
Are you back? The price is the same as the last three times.

27:18.785 --> 27:22.205
You bring a school principal here changes nothing.

27:22.288 --> 27:26.834
It's my mother, Bobby. She wanted to meet The Evangelist.

27:26.918 --> 27:30.880
Call him Princess if you want, but you still have to pay first.

27:30.963 --> 27:34.258
Before that, he named Hell's horse.

27:34.341 --> 27:37.636
So you have money with you?

27:37.928 --> 27:43.183
Otherwise it adjöken. I have to work out this evil bastard.

27:46.686 --> 27:49.898
I'm not crazy, mom. I promise.

27:56.613 --> 28:01.617
Good boy! So it should look like! Do not stop now!

28:03.536 --> 28:07.331
- What is the problem, Bobby? - The coach did not show up.

28:07.415 --> 28:11.794
He was the fifth that got cold feet when it comes to this horse.

28:11.877 --> 28:15.172
I can train him for you.

28:15.422 --> 28:21.720
Thanks for the offer, but the coaches pulled out for a reason.

28:21.803 --> 28:24.764
For the same reason as my shoulder injury.

28:24.848 --> 28:30.770
This bastard beats up anyone who comes near him.

28:31.020 --> 28:32.522
Come again!

28:32.605 --> 28:35.942
I can tame him. I know that.

28:36.025 --> 28:43.032
I mean no offense, but this horse is not for sweet little girls.

28:44.575 --> 28:48.495
You do not have ... the guts.

28:49.288 --> 28:50.873
We should go.

28:50.956 --> 28:55.544
I do not know how it is with the stake, but my balls are big enough.

28:59.840 --> 29:02.342
How about a bet?

29:02.425 --> 29:06.721
If I manage to remain in the saddle, you cut half the price.

29:06.805 --> 29:09.807
- A third. - Settled.

29:09.933 --> 29:13.227
But you must do more than talk.

29:16.022 --> 29:19.233
Debi! Please, be careful.

29:19.317 --> 29:25.406
Do not forget that if you hurt him, you must buy him.

29:25.489 --> 29:27.658
