29:29.076 --> 29:31.745
You remember me?

29:31.829 --> 29:36.750
We were meant to be together, then you galloped towards me.

29:36.833 --> 29:43.548
They think we are losers, but we will show them everything, right?

29:43.631 --> 29:49.637
We will succeed and will show them how to do it.

30:27.298 --> 30:29.675
Be careful with my horse, damn!

30:29.926 --> 30:33.262
- Please, do not swear. - Yes Lady...

30:33.346 --> 30:36.891
Slowly but surely. Do not forget me in front of my mother.

30:55.659 --> 31:01.414
- Are you going to keep your end of the agreement? - I can hardly believe my eyes.

31:01.497 --> 31:05.626
I knew the bastard was quick, but Satan!

31:05.710 --> 31:09.005
I did not know he was part kangaroo.

31:09.088 --> 31:15.511
It's great. I can get the money on ... four months.

31:15.761 --> 31:21.350
A contract is a contract, but it does not apply to life.

31:21.433 --> 31:26.897
- Okay, I just need some time ... - It's not my problem, ma'am.

31:26.980 --> 31:33.194
