31:33.278 --> 31:38.032
- I understand, but I ... - Today will be good. We have the money.

31:39.909 --> 31:44.622
Debi, I can not touch the money that your father has put aside for you.

31:44.705 --> 31:49.126
But I've saved up some money -

31:49.210 --> 31:52.463
- A sewing machine that can be used to embroidery.

31:52.546 --> 31:58.760
It's my money that I earned. Your father has no control over them.

31:58.844 --> 32:02.931
No, Mom. I can not receive them.

32:03.014 --> 32:06.184
You have wanted to buy the sewing machine for several years.

32:06.268 --> 32:12.607
Listen to what I say. If the Lord wants you to have this horse ...

32:12.690 --> 32:17.403
Not in this way. No problem.

32:17.487 --> 32:21.115
You have already sacrificed so much for my sake and Peggy.

32:21.199 --> 32:25.661
Okay okay! Take the poor wretch only!

32:25.745 --> 32:31.166
You two are more than one man can handle.

32:32.709 --> 32:38.548
If he proves able to compete, you can pay me later.

32:38.632 --> 32:42.302
No! No! Gently!

32:42.385 --> 32:47.140
